{"tid":910120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環鬧市驚現UFO 光點波浪形飄20秒","createTime":"2018-11-21T02:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T03:16:04.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"456d63172b7f25932be95b093e04dba16102003b","tid":910120,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:17:47.000Z","msg":"不明飛行物體驚現中環鬧市上空！讀者吳先生向東網爆料，昨晚(19日)於解放軍駐港部隊大廈上空發現疑似UFO，但不足20秒便消失眼前，「真係好誇張，好離奇！」他指當時不止自己目睹奇景，「有個的士司機都睇到，仲睇到『定晒格』」。<br />\n<br />\n吳先生指，以往都曾有疑似目擊UFO的經歷，但遠遠比不上今次來得震憾：「有好多個光點，形狀係類似波浪形，現場睇真係好立體，好近」。事發至今已快一天，他仍未能平伏心情，腦海中不斷回想昨晚的景況，更嘗試找出一個合理解釋，「我有諗過係咪無人機演練，但應該唔會係鬧市(演練)」。<br />\n<br />\n他認為昨晚的經歷非常珍貴，表示「我都想(UFO)係真！」東網向天文台查詢，獲覆至今未接獲市民關於UFO的報告。"},{"pid":"99c24c655a83b80e8c87468dc2e0439f0aa6a605","tid":910120,"uid":166827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:19:41.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"4cb05c5a5e0f788e6b867cdfba9a725860e8e0af","tid":910120,"uid":158613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:21:03.000Z","msg":"有mothership 添呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f829403f93eb8628bf66496c0b3b1293acb9763","tid":910120,"uid":202412,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:23:37.000Z","msg":"無圖無source 你話你見到IFC識飛都得啦"},{"pid":"44c0c37104e8032c4e47d71e850fcee5436a7631","tid":910120,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:26:56.000Z","msg":"天滅支共"},{"pid":"5fb4f9d4fa56628b1748d4bf015679618c628e29","tid":910120,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g